{"amendement": {"@xmlns": "http://schemas.assemblee-nationale.fr/referentiel", "uid": "AMANR5L17PO838901BTC0629P0D1N000054", "chronotag": "1739874701245", "legislature": "17", "identification": {"numeroLong": "54", "numeroOrdreDepot": "54", "prefixeOrganeExamen": "AN", "numeroRect": "0"}, "examenRef": "EXANR5L17PO838901BTC0629P0D1", "texteLegislatifRef": "PIONANR5L17BTC0629", "triAmendement": "biaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaao", "cardinaliteAmdtMultiples": "1", "amendementParentRef": "AMANR5L17PO838901BTC0629P0D1N000041", "signataires": {"auteur": {"typeAuteur": "D\u00e9put\u00e9", "gouvernementRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "acteurRef": "PA722366", "groupePolitiqueRef": "PO845407", "auteurRapporteurOrganeRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "cosignataires": {"acteurRef": ["PA719388", "PA721852"]}, "suffixe": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "libelle": "M.&#160;Fugit,  Mme&#160;Le&#160;Meur et Mme&#160;Lebec"}, "pointeurFragmentTexte": {"partieAmendableRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "division": {"titre": "Article PREMIER", "articleDesignationCourte": "ART. PREMIER", "articleDesignation": "ARTICLE PREMIER", "type": "ARTICLE", "avant_A_Apres": "A", "divisionRattachee": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "articleAdditionnel": "false", "chapitreAdditionnel": "false", "urlDivisionTexteVise": "/17/textes/0629.asp#D_Article_1er"}, "amendementStandard": {"alinea": {"avant_A_Apres": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "numero": "6", "alineaDesignation": "Alin\u00e9a 6"}}}, "corps": {"cartoucheInformatif": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenuAuteur": {"dispositif": "<p>I. &#x2013; &#x00C0; l&#x2019;alin&#x00E9;a 4, supprimer le mot : <br>&#x00AB; constantes &#x00BB;.<br>II. &#x2013; En cons&#x00E9;quence, &#x00E0; la fin du m&#x00EA;me alin&#x00E9;a 4, supprimer les mots :<br>&#x00AB; dans les parties communes &#x00BB;.</p>", "avantAppel": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "exposeSommaire": "<p>Le sous-amendement supprime la mention &#x00AB; constantes &#x00BB;, qui est impr&#x00E9;cise, ainsi que celle des parties communes, qui pourraient exclure certains travaux que nous souhaiterions justement voir vis&#x00E9;s par le pr&#x00E9;sent article.</p><p>- le mot \"constantes\" implique une sorte d'obligation pour le copropri&#x00E9;taire de relancer le syndic toutes les semaines et de demander la tenue d'une AG extraordinaire tous les mois, ce qui peut perturber le fonctionnement de la copropri&#x00E9;t&#x00E9; ; dans tous les cas, on se place dans l'hypoth&#x00E8;se o&#x00F9; la copropri&#x00E9;t&#x00E9; a d&#x00E9;j&#x00E0; examin&#x00E9; le point en AG et refus&#x00E9; les travaux ;</p><p>- les mots \"dans les parties communes\" semblent exclure les travaux privatifs d'int&#x00E9;r&#x00EA;t collectif (exemple : changement de fen&#x00EA;tres), ce qui est contre-productif.</p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2025-01-28", "datePublication": "2025-01-28", "soumisArticle40": "false", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "RT", "libelle": "Retir\u00e9"}, "sousEtat": {"code": "RT", "libelle": "Retir\u00e9 apr\u00e8s publication"}}, "dateSort": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "sort": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO838901BTC0629P0D1N000054?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionCommune": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionIdentique": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "accordGouvernementDepotHorsDelai": "Sans objet"}}